" - [#2]: The Brazilian Indigenous Constellations by Germano Bruno Afonso (Portugese). [PDF](http://www.telescopiosnaescola.pro.br/indigenas.pdf)"
msgstr ""
" - [#1]: The Tupi People. [Wikipedia-artikel](http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tupi_people)\n"
" - [#2]: de Braziliaanse inheemse sterrenbeelden door Germano Bruno Afonso (Portugees). [PDF](http://www.telescopiosnaescola.pro.br/indigenas.pdf)"

